  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add grated carrot and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add Cheonggukjang and cook, stirring constantly, until heated through, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add potatoes, apples, caraway seeds, and miso paste. Stir to combine.",
